# 🤖 Future Feature — AI 3D Model Generator

## Overview

This is a future Roblox Buddy AI feature.

It will NOT be available during the first launch.

It is planned for a future major update.

---

# Goal

Allow players to create professional 3D models without knowing 3D software.

Everything should happen using AI.

---

# Image → 3D Model

Players can upload an image.

Examples:

- Chair
- Table
- Car
- House
- Tree
- Sword
- Character
- Animal

AI automatically generates a complete 3D model.

---

# Text → 3D Model

Players type:

"Create a futuristic robot."

AI generates:

- 3D Mesh
- Materials
- Texture
- Scale
- Collision

---

# Drawing → 3D Model

Players draw a simple sketch.

AI converts it into a complete 3D object.

---

# Voice → 3D Model

Players speak:

"I want a flying pirate ship."

AI generates it.

---

# Style Converter

Players may convert styles.

Examples:

Realistic

↓

Roblox Style

Cartoon

↓

Roblox Style

Anime

↓

Low Poly

Voxel

↓

Modern

---

# Automatic Optimization

AI automatically creates multiple versions.

Examples:

Ultra Quality

↓

Medium Quality

↓

Low-End Version

This allows every device to use the same model.

---

# Mobile Optimization

AI automatically:

- Reduces polygons
- Compresses textures
- Optimizes materials
- Optimizes physics

Designed for smooth gameplay on low-end phones.

---

# Automatic Collision

AI creates collision automatically.

Players do not need to configure it manually.

---

# Automatic Animation

Supported models receive:

- Idle
- Walk
- Run
- Attack
- Jump
- Death

Generated automatically.

---

# Material Generator

Players may change materials.

Examples:

Wood

Metal

Stone

Ice

Fire

Crystal

Plastic

Glass

Gold

---

# Texture Generator

AI can generate textures.

Examples:

Wood Texture

Stone Texture

Brick Texture

Snow Texture

Lava Texture

Grass Texture

---

# AI Object Editor

Players can request edits.

Examples:

"Make it bigger."

"Make it red."

"Add wings."

"Remove the wheels."

"Turn it into Roblox style."

AI edits the existing model.

---

# AI Asset Optimizer

One-click optimization.

AI checks:

- Polygon Count
- Texture Size
- Memory Usage
- Physics Cost

Then automatically optimizes the asset.

---

# Copyright Protection

Uploaded images are scanned.

If copyrighted content is detected,

AI warns the player.

Only original or permitted assets may be published.

---

# Future Marketplace Integration

Creators can publish AI-generated assets.

Other players can:

- Preview
- Download
- Purchase
- Rate
- Review

---

